'''Bid Zard-e Olya''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0628><U+064A><U+062F><U+0632><U+0631><U+062F><U+0639><U+0644><U+064A><U+0627>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''B<U+012B>d Zard-e <U+2018>Oly<U+0101>'''; also known as '''B<U+012B>d Zard-e B<U+0101>l<U+0101>''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3056373|Bid Zard-e Olya}}</ref> is a village in [[Bid Zard Rural District]], in the [[Central District (Shiraz County)|Central District]] of [[Shiraz County]], [[Fars Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 1,206, in 295 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|07}}</ref>  

